# Reference disassembly — the commented reverse-engineered source of Atari's
# Asteroids (1979). A derivative of copyrighted code, kept purely as a local
# learning/reference quarry. NEVER committed or pushed.
#
# A-17: the *ported* ROM data tables (reference/*.ts) ARE committed — they are
# derived numeric tables, not the copyrighted source. Only the raw disassembly
# quarry (subdirs, listings) stays ignored, so ignore the contents of reference/
# but re-include the ported .ts tables.
reference/*
!reference/*.ts

# Audio assets — baked/served separately (e.g. Cloudflare R2), not committed
sfx/
